  }, "v4"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c tr\u1EBB th\u01A1 b\u1ECB kh\xE1t n\u01B0\u1EDBc l\u01B0\u1EE1i ch\xFAng d\xEDnh n\u01A1i v\xF2m h\u1ECDng. Tr\u1EBB con \u0111i xin b\xE1nh, nh\u01B0ng ch\u1EB3ng ai cho. "), mdx("h6", {
