  }, "v17"), mdx("p", null, "Ngo\xE0i ra, m\u1EAFt ch\xFAng ta \u0111\xE3 m\xF2n m\u1ECFi, tr\xF4ng ch\u1EDD v\xE0o m\u1ED9t s\u1EF1 c\u1EE9u gi\xFAp kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD \u0111\u1EBFn. T\u1EEB c\xE1c v\u1ECDng canh ch\xFAng ta tr\xF4ng ch\u1EEBng, mong c\xF3 d\xE2n n\xE0o \u0111\u1EBFn c\u1EE9u ch\xFAng ta. "), mdx("h6", {
