  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u1EEFng k\u1EBB r\u01B0\u1EE3t \u0111u\u1ED5i ch\xFAng ta nhanh h\u01A1n chim \u01B0ng tr\xEAn tr\u1EDDi. Ch\xFAng \u0111u\u1ED5i ch\xFAng ta v\xE0o trong n\xFAi v\xE0 ph\u1EE5c k\xEDch ch\xFAng ta trong sa m\u1EA1c. "), mdx("h6", {
